School of Professional Studies Divisions and Departments

Website listing the divisions and departments in NYUSPS. NYUSPS is made up the Center for Applied Liberal Arts, Center for Global Affairs, Center for Publishing, Division of Applied Undergraduate Studies, Division of Programs in Business, English Language Institute, Jonathan M. Tisch Center of Hospitality, Preston Robert Tisch Institute for Global Sport, and the Schack Institute of Real Estate. Each division page is divided into programs, which consists of degree details containing course descriptions for required and elective courses for each degree.
